## 2. Educational Content - Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International

The educational content in the `public/content/` directory is an Icelandic
translation and adaptation of "Chemistry 2e" by OpenStax, originally available at:
https://openstax.org/details/books/chemistry-2e

Original Work:
- Title: Chemistry 2e
- Authors: Paul Flowers, Klaus Theopold, Richard Langley, William R. Robinson
- Publisher: OpenStax
- Original License: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)
- Original Source: https://openstax.org/details/books/chemistry-2e

This translated and adapted content is licensed under the Creative Commons
Attribution 4.0 International License (CC BY 4.0).

